{"tid":1494482,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯油尖旺區議會主席葉傲冬知法犯法","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T06:42:03.000Z","uid":224992,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e29d5ce35f83ef0e5f368b2d5cfafcae2993244","tid":1494482,"uid":224992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"民建聯油尖旺區議會主席葉傲冬知法犯法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFigcv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFigcv7.jpg&h=6b95ddb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8ZyZa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8ZyZa7.jpg&h=f4db141f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片攝於昨天8月20日<br />\n葉傲冬身為油尖旺區議會主席除左唔俾討論反送中，仲知法犯法？<br />\n你捧隻豬出來都算<br />\n咁樣單頭都得?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據地政總署2019年5月31日生效的路旁展示非商業宣傳品管理計劃實施指引的附註，其中第7(b)(ii)項關於「主要受惠者」的準則，指出獲分配展示點的個人/團體的名字/名稱及/或頭像，如出現在橫額上，而所佔尺寸不小於同列在橫額的各個其他人士或團體，該人/團體會視為主要受惠者。<br />\n<br />\n其實一般市民可以點告?  係唔係純粹可以投訴?"},{"pid":"82d63f70d24e96adb221fbca262e87321da8fed0","tid":1494482,"uid":57567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"1823咗先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9913eeaf5c66ee3fff91ff2a0d09440bd41503b4","tid":1494482,"uid":52828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf60267221cb771885aade0bdac08a2d3fd4d125","tid":1494482,"uid":224992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"HA Secrets再爆料 暗指葉國謙侄(葉傲冬)有份「安排」譚耀宗割瘜肉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/ha-secret%E5%86%8D%E7%88%86%E6%96%99%E6%9A%97%E6%8C%87%E8%91%89%E5%9C%8B%E8%AC%99%E4%BE%84%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD-%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92-%E8%AD%9A%E8%80%80%E5%AE%97%E5%89%B2%E7%98%9C%E8%82%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fha-secret%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2588%2586